Description: This package provides helper functions for downloading and manipulating North American Breeding Bird Survey (BBS) data and metadata from the U.S. Geological Survey. The functionality streamlines this the process by which these data are accessed, downloaded locally, and imported into R.Depends: R (>= 3.5.1).  
